Read config file

The thought here is to return a list where the names hew as closely as possible to the names in the standard.

ct_read_config(file)

Arguments

file

character, single line, path to a file or a single string

Value

list, specified in vignette("config")

Examples

  ct_example("keating_1999.CFG") %>%
  ct_read_config()
